                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-392-18550226 t18550226-392-punishment-71"></join>Confined Twelve Months</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Common Serjeant.</hi>
